name: Super Suicide Girl
description:
No girl committed suicide during the development of this game

An interesting and challenging platformer game. What does this do? Anything can happen! Enjoy 50+ screens split between 5 thematic worlds with different mechanics and challenges. Don't let this little girl die!

Made with SDL2 on C++

If you play tag me on twitter @Toxapez with your save file!

Press F for fullscreen Press R for level reset
